    "body": "<img width=\"3131\" height=\"469\" alt=\"Image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/3417513c-dd5a-4329-b0d7-744efb8f4d24\" />\n\nCurrently, a local value is presented by [LocalState](https://doc.rust-lang.org/nightly/nightly-rustc/rustc_const_eval/interpret/struct.LocalState.html) which distinguishes the value as an [Operand](https://doc.rust-lang.org/nightly/nightly-rustc/rustc_const_eval/interpret/operand/enum.Operand.html) (Immediate vs Indirect). \n\nBut since the Rust type can be known, we can show the intepreted value based on the type.",
